Package se.miun.itm.input.util.sql

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDatabaseConnector
    A skeletal implementation of the interface DatabaseConnector.
    DatabaseAdapter
    Used for performing SQL database transactions such as export, import, updating and deletion of Document:s and Exportable:s.
    DatabaseAdapter.DummyLock
    A dummy Lock whose methods are no-ops.
    DatabaseDeleter
    Used for deleting Document:s and Exportable:s from SQL databases.
    DatabaseInitializer
    Used for creating the InPUT SQL schema in databases.
    DatabaseUpdater
    Used for updating Document:s and Exportable:s in SQL databases.
    Table
    Represents an immutable SQL table.
    Table.ColumnMetaDatum
    An immutable metadatum about a SQL table column.
    Table.Entry<T>
    Represents an immutable SQL table entry.
    Table.Row
    Represents an immutable SQL table row.
    Types
    An uninstantiable class with a static immutable Map that maps the names of all fields of the class Types into their values.
